Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在幹什麼啊 小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把夕子學姐交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把夕子學姐交出來..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被殺掉..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所有人都會被殺掉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夕子學姐幹的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從窗口跑出來繞到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夕子學姐沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真可惜 還差一點就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒做過自我介紹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做桐島有子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個學校 夕子這個名字代表著什麼樣的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.73,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,610)}有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 討厭迷信怪談的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭散佈怪談的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有..我最討厭你們這樣沒事找事的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼事比把你們統統摧毀更加令人愉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的騷動 是妳設計的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐什麼的消失了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺死怪談！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說那孩子也是“夕子”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~ 好可怕~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了它..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子！這孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為害怕怪談中的夕子學姐而很困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想同為“夕子”的妳應該會知道點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了我不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪談!？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真相信有這事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些人..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦子都出問題了吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也 也是呢......
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪什麼的 不可能真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是害怕的東西還是會害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也都是這麼想的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了它..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(235,160)}回妳的舊校舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,480)}快點成佛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(875,540)}別來學校了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1105,180)}消失吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了它..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪談什麼的..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺了它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺了你們..無論是怪談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是相信怪談的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家..全都..全都！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妳們..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子 怎麼辦啊 有子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到夕子學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會被紅人殺掉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 紅人要殺的是夕子學姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說紅人在找夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在尋找活祭品的夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人要殺的是夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活祭品的夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.13,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,610)}有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人要殺的是夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要夕子學姐死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.59,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(573,610)}有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼我都會保護妳們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.38,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(693,610)}有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對..是夕子學姐才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死怪談..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳覺得這種事真的能做得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 夕子學姐被紅人殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這個傳聞散播開來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能行得通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐妳覺得這樣就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好不好的..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這是那孩子的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就沒有阻止她的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟她被別人欺負都是因為我的存在的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會怨恨我是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這種事太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐不會難過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難過是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐島有子被當成紅人的活祭品了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為紅人不是桐島同學假扮的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們受傳聞影響太深 精神變得不正常了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話不知道會做出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那孩子是因為怨恨我才..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 夕子學姐也一定要救一救桐島同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我不是夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是什麼活祭品！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 這樣我就不會被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人會饒過我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 好像沒人發現所以我來告訴你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人的真面目其實就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我設計出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你們在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們了 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼夕子學姐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼紅人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕那種不存在的東西而被妄想所控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真的傻不傻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人是存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是如此的害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以夕子學姐..活祭品是必須的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把夕子學姐交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有人會被襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再擔驚受怕地過日子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活祭品是幹什麼用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人在尋求著夕子學姐的鮮血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐的鮮血？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了把外套染紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要犧牲掉夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就能被原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐會拯救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是要為此而犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐就是為此而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐會拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人想死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死掉..不想死掉..不想死掉..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要讓夕子學姐流血的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把夕子學姐獻上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於能安心入睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於能集中精力學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一放心肚子就餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了夕子學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為夕子學姐會為了我們而流血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯為了我們獻出自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不會對我們見死不救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她是夕子學姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都相信夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所·以才會被紅人選上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所·以才在尋找夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他渴望著夕子學姐的鮮血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人馬上就會來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐會從怪談變成傳說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能保護大家她很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐會拯救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把夕子學姐的鮮血給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流血吧 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只要妳流血 大家就會變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紅人..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用虛假的貢品欺騙我的罪行很沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用鮮血來償還吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被殺死了 救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死 我不想死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我看見了 那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是舊校舍的幽靈..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來..救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不害怕怪談嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？不..怕倒是不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對桐島同學來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐說不定是妳仇恨的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真正的夕子學姐不是可怕的怪談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少你不會說我是夕子學姐對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 剛才我說了那麼臭屁的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是貞一對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問..霧江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把它敲響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？嘛稍微製造一點恐怖效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？也就是惡作劇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是惡作劇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了啦 不快點逃走的話老師就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧江同學快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因銘刻之名而顯己之存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因映目之影而識己之真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想忘卻好想忘卻..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋須害怕..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪之七 忘卻少女
